data.description: Welcome to 3831 Kendall Brook Drive. Step into a world of refined elegance and modern convenience in this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroomresidence. This captivating home boasts an open and split floor plan, seamlessly blending spacious living areas with a touch of contemporary charm. The expansivekitchen, adorned with granite countertops and a handy breakfast bar, invites culinary creativity and casual gatherings. Luxurious touches abound, from the gleamingtile and LVP flooring to the expansive foyer that sets the stage for grand entrances. Unwind and rejuvenate in the tranquil primary suite, featuring a dual vanity, aluxurious soaking tub, a separate shower, and a generous walk-in closet. Step outside to the covered back porch, an idyllic retreat for alfresco dining or quietmoments amidst nature's embrace. The private fenced lot provides a secure haven for outdoor play and relaxation. This exceptional property qualifies for USDAfinancing, making it even more attainable for qualified buyers to realize their dreams of homeownership. With its impeccable design, thoughtful amenities, and aserene setting, this residence is a haven for those who seek a lifestyle of comfort and style. All information provided is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer orbuyer’s agent to verify all information.
